text: Tsepang Gladys Sello (born February 23, 1997) is a Mosotho middle-distance runner. She competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in the women's 800 metres race; her time of 2:10.22 in the heats did not qualify her for the semifinals. ==References== Category:1997 births Category:Living people Category:Lesotho female middle-distance runners Category:Olympic athletes of Lesotho Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2014 Summer Youth Olympics Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Olympics Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2018 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for Lesotho Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2019 African Games
